class Solution(object):
    def postorderTraversal(self, root):
        """
        :type root: TreeNode
        :rtype: List[int]
        """
        
        if root is None:
            return []
        
        stack = [root]
        result = []
        
        while stack:
            node = stack.pop()
            result.append(node.val)
            
            if node.left:

            if node.right:
                stack.append(node.right)
                
        return result[::-1]
